This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) because it deals with natural language processing and the semantic representation of language. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) because it involves neural network-based models for learning embeddings. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) because it involves the training of neural networks. It could also be classified under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) because it involves the use of neural networks. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.CC (Computational Complexity) because it deals with the complexity of logical reasoning.
